name: New Yrs Collection Set
description:
Shine as bright as the stars and steal the spotlight this New Year's Eve! 

You will receive all four full size bottles of polish in this collection for less bling. 

*Atomic Afterglow is a black tinted glitter polish with black squares, black and gunmetal hexes and eye catching holographic glitters in assorted shapes and sizes. Two or three coats displays the black base best. 

*Gimme Shimmy is a steel colored, slighty textured polish. Micro glitter in a holographic finish gives it a shimmery look. Two to three coats gives the textured finish. 

*Smokey Sprinkle features a clear base with assorted sizes and shapes of smokey, gunmetal glitter. Looks amazing over a dark or black polish.

*Glimmer Glamour is a foggy gray base jelly polish that features an assortment of holographic silvery glitters. Two or more coats shows the base color the best or layered over a gray for a finished look.

name: OrnaMint
description:
Decorating the tree with colorful delight.

OrnaMint is a spearmint colored jelly polish that's packed with bold glitters in foil, shimmer and matte finishes in assorted shapes and sizes.

Slight variations may occur during shipping so gently roll the polish between your palms to get the glitter moving.

name: Ooh no, Frosty!
description:
Ooh no Frosty, I think it might a tad too warm for you.

Ooh no, Frosty! is a bone white crelly polish full of matte glitters such as black, green, red and white in assorted shaped glitters. No way Frosty would survive this Texas weather so this is what's left of him :)

Slight variations may occur during shipping so gently roll the polish between your palms to get the glitter moving.

name: Christmas Trinkets
description:
A Christmas Trinket is a memory to cherish always.

Christmas Trinkets is a red based jelly polish packed with red foil stars, large red hexes, and assorted green hexes & dots.

Slight variations may occur during shipping so gently roll the polish between your palms to get the glitter moving.

name: Uh oh, Rudolph!
description:
You know what they say about yellow snow?! :) 

Uh oh Rudolph is a off white crelly polish filled with gold & silver hexes, matte white dots, large red foil dots & bits of silver and gold glitter.

Slight variations may occur during shipping so gently roll the polish between your palms to get the glitter moving.

name: Holo Jolly Christmas
description:
"Have a Holo Jolly Christmas, it's the best time of the year"

 Holo Jolly Christmas is a holo micro glitter polish with twinkling red, green and gold glitters in assorted shapes and sizes. This beauty flashes all sorts of spectacular colors in the light.

Slight variations may occur during shipping so gently roll the polish between your palms to get the glitter moving.

name: Mistletoe Kiss & Cranberry Kiss Combo.
description:
This gorgeous combo consists of two textured polishes. Mistletoe Kiss is a beautiful hunter green with gold holo and Cranberry Kiss is a gorgeous crimson color with scattered silver holo.

Apply two light coats to achieve the textured finish, use top coat for a smooth shine.

Slight variations may occur during shipping so gently roll the polish between your palms to get the glitter moving.

name: Fairy Fallout
description:
Tons of holographic goodness here, Fairy Fallout can be used as a topper to enhance plain polish or worn alone using two coats for full coverage. Assorted shapes and sizes of silver holo glitters.  

Two coats swatches are shown over black and clear. 

Slight variations may occur during shipping so gently roll the polish between your palms to get the glitter moving.
